    "SSEHCET structure evaluationThe case study allowed us to examine SSDMM's applicability in a real-world setting.",
    "The respondents of the case study were also asked to evaluate the structure of SSEHCET.",
    "The evaluation of structure involves three dimensions: self-explanatory, applicable, and the distribution of technologies at various layers.According to the statistics presented in Fig. 13, the weighted average score for each question related to the SSEHCET structure was more than 3.5.",
